Invocation Name: cooper hewitt
des:
Welcome to Cooper Hewitt, Smithsonian Design Museum! 

Virtually visit America’s design museum through vivid visual descriptions as you tour the galleries exploring design narratives across centuries. Learn more about individual works, designers’ processes, and immerse yourself in the historic architecture of the landmark Carnegie Mansion.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
